
---


@startuml
' Define package if needed (optional)
package "Celebrations Organization System" {
    ' Core Entities
    class User {
        +String firstName
        +String lastName
        +String email (PK)
        +String password
        +String postalAddress
        +String phoneNumber
    }

    class Organizer extends User {
        +Event[] events
        +void inviteAttendee(Attendee attendee)
        +void createEvent(Event event)
        +void manageChecklist(Task task)
    }

    class Attendee extends User {
        +Event[] eventsAttending
        +void respondToInvitation(String response)
        +void selectTask(Task task)
    }

    class Event {
        +String name
        +DateTime startDate
        +DateTime endDate
        +String occasion
        +Location location
        +List<Organizer> organizers
        +List<Attendee> attendees
        +Checklist checklist
        +int totalConfirmed
        +int totalMaybe
        +int totalDeclined
        +int totalNoResponse
    }

    class Location {
        +String name
        +String address
    }

    class Checklist {
        +List<Task> tasks
        +void addTask(Task task)
        +void markTaskStatus(Task task, String status)
    }

    class Task {
        +String description
        +String status  // e.g., To Do, Done, Not Applicable
        +Boolean assignedToAttendee
        +Attendee assignedAttendee
    }

    class EventType {
        +String typeName
    }
}

' Relationships
User <|-- Organizer
User <|-- Attendee

Event "0..*" -- "1" EventType : has type
Event "1" -- "1" Location : is located at
Event "1" -- "*" Checklist : has
Event "1" -- "*" Organizer : managed by
Event "1" -- "*" Attendee : attended by

Checklist "1" -- "*" Task : contains
Task "1" -- "0..1" Attendee : assigned to

@enduml

---

### 📌 Notes:

- **User** is an abstract class extended by both `Organizer` and `Attendee`.
- **Event** can have multiple organizers and attendees.
- **Checklist** is part of each event and includes a list of **Tasks**.
- **Task** may be assigned to an **Attendee**, which allows tracking what each attendee brings or does.
- **EventType** is used to categorize events (e.g., birthday, graduation).
- **Location** can be reused across events.

